Description
Source

misspell-en

misspell-en is a espanso package which is replacing commonly misspelled english words. The package is based on github.com/client9/misspell.

Installation

Install the package with:
espanso install misspell-en

Usage

Type
yuo
and see what's happening.

License

BSD 3-Clause "New" or "Revised" License
